OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1776352251
OL,3,CNeighbours 'forgotten' a year on from
OL,4,Cfatal house explosion
OL,6,FPeople who live on a street in Worksop
OL,7,Fwhere a house exploded say they feel
OL,8,F"forgotten" as the site remains a pile
OL,9,Fof rubble a year on from the blast.
OL,11,FThe terraced property on John Street
OL,12,Fexploded on 12 April 2025, killing 53-
OL,13,Fyear-old David Howard.
OL,15,FAn inquest last month found he had
OL,16,Fbeen struggling with mental health and
OL,17,Fdrugs and blew up the house himself
OL,18,Fafter hearing his rent was being
OL,19,Fincreased.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1776352251
OL,3,CNeighbours 'forgotten' a year on from
OL,4,Cfatal house explosion
OL,6,FThe council cleared some of the debris
OL,7,Ffrom the blast in the weeks afterwards
OL,8,Fto make the site safe, but insurance
OL,9,Fdelays have held up any further work.
OL,11,FJane Revill lives four doors away. Her
OL,12,Fproperty was one of a number of
OL,13,Fsurrounding houses damaged by the
OL,14,Fblast.
OL,16,FShe said: "It blew windows open, bent
OL,17,Fhinges on doors and windows. The night
OL,18,Fof the explosion we were out - we'd
OL,19,Fgone for a meal.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1776352251
OL,3,CNeighbours 'forgotten' a year on from
OL,4,Cfatal house explosion
OL,6,F"My neighbour rang and said what had
OL,7,Fhappened. We rushed back and within
OL,8,Fminutes all hell had broken loose.
OL,9,FDevastation."
OL,11,FJane had to claim on her home
OL,12,Finsurance to cover the repairs to her
OL,13,Fhouse and her premium has since
OL,14,Fdoubled.
OL,16,FShe and other neighbours are also left
OL,17,Fwith a view of the rubble from their
OL,18,Fback gardens.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1776352251
OL,3,CNeighbours 'forgotten' a year on from
OL,4,Cfatal house explosion
OL,6,FJane said: "Visually it's awful. And
OL,7,Fit's something that I see on a day-to-
OL,8,Fday basis. Can't get away from it. I
OL,9,Fjust feel that we're forgotten.
OL,11,F"It's just an awful situation to be
OL,12,Fin. This is my community and it's just
OL,13,Fbeen devastated."
OL,15,FRob Gardener's house was also damaged.
OL,16,FHe has recently put it up for sale,
OL,17,Fbut is worried potential buyers may be
OL,18,Fdeterred by the incident.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1776352251
OL,3,CNeighbours 'forgotten' a year on from
OL,4,Cfatal house explosion
OL,6,FHe said: "It was not very nice when it
OL,7,Fhappened and it's still not looking
OL,8,Fvery nice now. And I think it's about
OL,9,Ftime something was actually started
OL,10,Fand tidied up.
OL,12,F"I'd just like to see something done,
OL,13,Fsome work started, and then we can get
OL,14,Fsome idea of what's happening. Put
OL,15,Feveryone's mind at rest that it will
OL,16,Fbe a nice street again."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1776352251
OL,3,CNeighbours 'forgotten' a year on from
OL,4,Cfatal house explosion
OL,6,FIn the months since the explosion,
OL,7,Fplanning permission has been granted
OL,8,Ffor one of the two neighbouring
OL,9,Fproperties, which partially collapsed
OL,10,Fin the blast, to be rebuilt.
OL,12,FBut ITV News understands work on the
OL,13,Fhouse which exploded has been held up
OL,14,Fbecause insurers have had to wait
OL,15,Funtil the conclusion of the inquest
OL,16,Finto Mr Howard's death to proceed with
OL,17,Fthe owner's claim.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1776352251
OL,3,CNeighbours 'forgotten' a year on from
OL,4,Cfatal house explosion
OL,6,FThe owner, who asked not to be named,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Following the inquest we are
OL,8,Fwaiting for the insurers to act upon
OL,9,Fit."
OL,11,FBassetlaw District Council said it
OL,12,Funderstood the concerns of people
OL,13,Fliving on John Street and has a "great
OL,14,Fdeal of sympathy" for them.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1776352251
OL,3,CNeighbours 'forgotten' a year on from
OL,4,Cfatal house explosion
OL,6,FIn a statement it said: "As Bassetlaw
OL,7,FDistrict Council does not own the
OL,8,Fland, buildings or remains of any
OL,9,Fproperties that were affected by the
OL,10,Fexplosion, it is the responsibility of
OL,11,Flandlords, owners and their respective
OL,12,Finsurance companies to make
OL,13,Farrangements to clear or remediate the
OL,14,Fsite, or to take any further action on
OL,15,Fother buildings that may have been
OL,16,Faffected.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1776352251
OL,3,CNeighbours 'forgotten' a year on from
OL,4,Cfatal house explosion
OL,6,F"We are aware that a planning
OL,7,Fapplication has been granted for the
OL,8,Fsite of 24 John Street and that all
OL,9,Flandowners and insurance companies
OL,10,Fmust be given a reasonable time in
OL,11,Fwhich to resolve this complex
OL,12,Fsituation."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
